item.title: The Fellas Dive Into The Current State, And The Future Of The Economy, The Recent Supply Chain And Popup Competitors
item.description: Zach Peyton, founder of Superior Fence and Rail, is the president over all 86 franchises which are located across 30 states as of October, 2022. Zach breaks out as he likes to call it, "his cracked crystal ball", and dives into the economic swing and what he's seeing across the board with his established AND newly opened branches. Dan and Cannon discuss how these changes are affecting their fence businesses and what they are doing to manage during this economic correction... Feed: https://feeds.captivate.fm/my-fence-life/
